text: Marlene Steinherr (born 10 September 1985) is a German sailor specializing in the 470 (dinghy) class. She represented Germany, along with partner Annika Bochmann, in the women's 470 class at the 2016 Summer Olympics in Rio de Janeiro. They finished in 18th place. == References == Category:1985 births Category:Living people Category:German female sailors (sport) Category:Olympic sailors of Germany Category:Sailors at the 2016 Summer Olympics – 470
